    "body": "The need for sequential calls is the best use case I can think of. In current state,  sequential calls where re-entrancy is enforced leads to creation of two distinct transaction to be done on chain. But with Permissioned Re-entrancy sequential calls can be permitted by definition. One area where sequential calls will play a major role is in bridging contracts.  ",
